    NAME@{ub}
        @{"GA_TEXTEDITOR_ReadOnly" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/gadgets/texteditor.h/File" 56} -- [ISG], @{"BOOL" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/exec/types.h/File" 91}@{b}

    FUNCTION@{ub}
        This tag is not supported in the Reaction version. Use @{"GA_ReadOnly" LINK "gg:doc/NDK/Guide/Include/intuition/gadgetclass.h/File" 189} instead.

        In ReadOnly-mode there will be:
        No cursor (but a normal TAB-frame).
        TAB will activate the next gadget (instead of alt TAB).
        The frame will be set to a ReadListFrame. (may change).
        There is no ARexx support, except "Copy".

        The GA_TEXTEDITOR_StyleXXX tags are still useable.

